<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Fórum — Fênix</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@24,400,0,0" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg: #f4f4f4;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --surface2: #f5eeff;
      --border: #e0d0ec;
      --text: #2a1336;
      --text-muted: #7a6385;
      --text-dim: #a090b0;
      --primary: #3b1c4a;
      --primary-hover: #4e2661;
      --gold: #e6c27a;
      --upvote: #e6c27a;
      --downvote: #9b59b6;
      --header-h: 80px;
      --sidebar-w: 240px;
      --right-w: 300px;
    }

    .icon {
      font-family: 'Material Symbols Outlined';
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1;
      vertical-align: middle;
      user-select: none;
    }
    .icon-sm { font-size: 16px; }
    .icon-lg { font-size: 24px; }

    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI", system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .forum-layout {
      display: flex;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding-top: calc(var(--header-h) + 24px);
      padding-bottom: 40px;
      gap: 20px;
      padding-left: 16px;
      padding-right: 16px;
    }

    /* ── LEFT SIDEBAR ── */
    .sidebar-left {
      width: var(--sidebar-w);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      position: sticky;
      top: calc(var(--header-h) + 24px);
      height: calc(100vh - var(--header-h) - 24px);
      overflow-y: auto;
      scrollbar-width: none;
    }
    .sidebar-left::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

    .sidebar-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .sidebar-card-header {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: var(--gold);
      padding: 12px 14px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: background .15s;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .nav-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .nav-item:hover, .nav-item.active { background: var(--surface2); }
    .nav-item.active { font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); }

    .nav-icon {
      width: 30px; height: 30px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: var(--gold);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .nav-icon .icon { font-size: 17px; }

    /* ── MAIN FEED ── */
    .feed { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }

    .feed-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .feed-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .btn-nova-post {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 8px 18px;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: var(--gold);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background .15s;
    }
    .btn-nova-post:hover { background: var(--primary-hover); }

    .feed-controls {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .sort-btn {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
      padding: 7px 14px;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all .15s;
    }
    .sort-btn:hover { border-color: var(--primary); color: var(--primary); }
    .sort-btn.active { background: var(--primary); color: var(--gold); border-color: var(--primary); }
    .sort-btn.active .icon { color: var(--gold); }

    /* ── POST CARD ── */
    .post-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: border-color .15s, box-shadow .15s;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .post-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--primary);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(59,28,74,.1);
    }

    .post-inner {
      display: flex;
      padding: 12px;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .vote-col {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 36px;
    }

    .vote-btn {
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      padding: 2px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      line-height: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: color .1s;
    }
    .vote-btn .icon { font-size: 22px; }
    .vote-btn:hover.up { color: var(--upvote); }
    .vote-btn:hover.down { color: var(--downvote); }
    .vote-btn.voted-up { color: var(--upvote); }
    .vote-btn.voted-down { color: var(--downvote); }

    .vote-count {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .post-body { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }

    .post-meta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .post-category {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary);
      text-decoration: none;
      background: var(--surface2);
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .post-category .icon { font-size: 14px; }
    .post-category:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .meta-sep { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 10px; }
    .post-time { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .post-author { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); }

    .post-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .post-flair {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--surface2);
      color: var(--primary);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .post-excerpt {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      display: -webkit-box;
      -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
      line-clamp: 2;
      -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .post-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .action-btn {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
      padding: 5px 8px;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background .1s, color .1s;
    }
    .action-btn .icon { font-size: 16px; }
    .action-btn:hover { background: var(--surface2); color: var(--primary); }

    /* ── RIGHT SIDEBAR ── */
    .sidebar-right {
      width: var(--right-w);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      position: sticky;
      top: calc(var(--header-h) + 24px);
      height: fit-content;
    }

    .widget {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .widget-header {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: var(--gold);
      padding: 12px 16px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .widget-body { padding: 14px 16px; }

    .emergency-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .emergency-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .emergency-icon {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--surface2);
      color: var(--primary);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .emergency-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); }
    .emergency-number { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); }

    .rule-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 7px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      align-items: center;
    }
    .rule-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .rule-num { font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .rule-item a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
    .rule-item a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .forum-footer {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      line-height: 1.9;
      padding: 0 4px;
    }
    .forum-footer a { color: var(--text-dim); }

    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--border); border-radius: 3px; }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .sidebar-left { display: none; }
      .sidebar-right { display: none; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .forum-layout { padding-left: 8px; padding-right: 8px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<%- include('../partials/header2.ejs') %>

<div class="forum-layout">

  <!-- ── LEFT SIDEBAR ── -->
  <nav class="sidebar-left">
    <div class="sidebar-card">
      <div class="sidebar-card-header">Categorias</div>
      <a class="nav-item active" href="#">
        <div class="nav-icon"><span class="icon">home</span></div> Todos os tópicos
      </a>
      <a class="nav-item" href="#">
        <div class="nav-icon"><span class="icon">crisis_alert</span></div> Violência Doméstica
      </a>
      <a class="nav-item" href="#">
        <div class="nav-icon"><span class="icon">gavel</span></div> Direitos da Mulher
      </a>
      <a class="nav-item" href="#">
        <div class="nav-icon"><span class="icon">handshake</span></div> Buscar Apoio
      </a>
      <a class="nav-item" href="#">
        <div class="nav-icon"><span class="icon">forum</span></div> Relatos
      </a>
      <a class="nav-item" href="#">
        <div class="nav-icon"><span class="icon">psychology</span></div> Saúde Mental
      </a>
      <a class="nav-item" href="#">
        <div class="nav-icon"><span class="icon">business</span></div> ONGs
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ── MAIN FEED ── -->
  <main class="feed">
    <div class="feed-header">
      <h1 class="feed-title">
        <span class="icon icon-lg" style="color:var(--primary);">favorite</span>
        Fórum Fênix
      </h1>
      <button class="btn-nova-post">
        <span class="icon icon-sm">edit</span> Nova publicação
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="feed-controls">
      <button class="sort-btn active">
        <span class="icon icon-sm">local_fire_department</span> Em alta
      </button>
      <button class="sort-btn">
        <span class="icon icon-sm">schedule</span> Recentes
      </button>
      <button class="sort-btn">
        <span class="icon icon-sm">chat_bubble</span> Mais comentados
      </button>
    </div>

    <!-- POST 1 -->
    <article class="post-card">
      <div class="post-inner">
        <div class="vote-col">
          <button class="vote-btn up" onclick="vote(event,this,'up')"><span class="icon">keyboard_arrow_up</span></button>
          <span class="vote-count">245</span>
          <button class="vote-btn down" onclick="vote(event,this,'down')"><span class="icon">keyboard_arrow_down</span></button>
        </div>
        <div class="post-body">
          <div class="post-meta">
            <a class="post-category" href="#"><span class="icon">crisis_alert</span> Violência Doméstica</a>
            <span class="meta-sep">•</span>
            <span class="post-author">por usuária anônima</span>
            <span class="meta-sep">•</span>
            <span class="post-time">há 2 horas</span>
          </div>
          <span class="post-flair">Dúvida</span>
          <h2 class="post-title">Como denunciar violência doméstica com segurança e em sigilo?</h2>
          <p class="post-excerpt">Estou numa situação difícil e tenho medo de fazer a denúncia. Quero saber quais canais são mais seguros e se minha identidade fica protegida...</p>
          <div class="post-actions">
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">chat_bubble</span> 67 Comentários</button>
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">share</span> Compartilhar</button>
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">bookmark</span> Salvar</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- POST 2 -->
    <article class="post-card">
      <div class="post-inner">
        <div class="vote-col">
          <button class="vote-btn up" onclick="vote(event,this,'up')"><span class="icon">keyboard_arrow_up</span></button>
          <span class="vote-count">1,2 mil</span>
          <button class="vote-btn down" onclick="vote(event,this,'down')"><span class="icon">keyboard_arrow_down</span></button>
        </div>
        <div class="post-body">
          <div class="post-meta">
            <a class="post-category" href="#"><span class="icon">forum</span> Relatos</a>
            <span class="meta-sep">•</span>
            <span class="post-author">por Maria S.</span>
            <span class="meta-sep">•</span>
            <span class="post-time">há 1 dia</span>
          </div>
          <span class="post-flair">Relato</span>
          <h2 class="post-title">Consegui sair de uma situação de abuso com apoio de uma ONG — minha história</h2>
          <p class="post-excerpt">Quero compartilhar minha história para dar esperança a outras mulheres. Depois de 3 anos, encontrei apoio no projeto Recomeçar e hoje tenho uma nova vida...</p>
          <div class="post-actions">
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">chat_bubble</span> 134 Comentários</button>
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">share</span> Compartilhar</button>
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">bookmark</span> Salvar</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- POST 3 -->
    <article class="post-card">
      <div class="post-inner">
        <div class="vote-col">
          <button class="vote-btn up" onclick="vote(event,this,'up')"><span class="icon">keyboard_arrow_up</span></button>
          <span class="vote-count">89</span>
          <button class="vote-btn down" onclick="vote(event,this,'down')"><span class="icon">keyboard_arrow_down</span></button>
        </div>
        <div class="post-body">
          <div class="post-meta">
            <a class="post-category" href="#"><span class="icon">gavel</span> Direitos da Mulher</a>
            <span class="meta-sep">•</span>
            <span class="post-author">por Ana Lima</span>
            <span class="meta-sep">•</span>
            <span class="post-time">há 3 dias</span>
          </div>
          <span class="post-flair">Informação</span>
          <h2 class="post-title">Quais são meus direitos ao registrar um boletim de ocorrência por violência doméstica?</h2>
          <p class="post-excerpt">Muitas mulheres não sabem que têm direito a medidas protetivas imediatas, atendimento preferencial e acompanhamento especializado...</p>
          <div class="post-actions">
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">chat_bubble</span> 45 Comentários</button>
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">share</span> Compartilhar</button>
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">bookmark</span> Salvar</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- POST 4 -->
    <article class="post-card">
      <div class="post-inner">
        <div class="vote-col">
          <button class="vote-btn up" onclick="vote(event,this,'up')"><span class="icon">keyboard_arrow_up</span></button>
          <span class="vote-count">312</span>
          <button class="vote-btn down" onclick="vote(event,this,'down')"><span class="icon">keyboard_arrow_down</span></button>
        </div>
        <div class="post-body">
          <div class="post-meta">
            <a class="post-category" href="#"><span class="icon">psychology</span> Saúde Mental</a>
            <span class="meta-sep">•</span>
            <span class="post-author">por equipe Fênix</span>
            <span class="meta-sep">•</span>
            <span class="post-time">há 5 dias</span>
          </div>
          <span class="post-flair">Recurso</span>
          <h2 class="post-title">Lista de serviços gratuitos de saúde mental para mulheres em situação de vulnerabilidade</h2>
          <p class="post-excerpt">Compilamos uma lista com CVV, CAPS, CRAS e outros serviços totalmente gratuitos disponíveis em todo o Brasil. Nenhuma mulher precisa passar por isso sozinha...</p>
          <div class="post-actions">
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">chat_bubble</span> 28 Comentários</button>
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">share</span> Compartilhar</button>
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">bookmark</span> Salvar</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- POST 5 -->
    <article class="post-card">
      <div class="post-inner">
        <div class="vote-col">
          <button class="vote-btn up" onclick="vote(event,this,'up')"><span class="icon">keyboard_arrow_up</span></button>
          <span class="vote-count">57</span>
          <button class="vote-btn down" onclick="vote(event,this,'down')"><span class="icon">keyboard_arrow_down</span></button>
        </div>
        <div class="post-body">
          <div class="post-meta">
            <a class="post-category" href="#"><span class="icon">handshake</span> Buscar Apoio</a>
            <span class="meta-sep">•</span>
            <span class="post-author">por usuária anônima</span>
            <span class="meta-sep">•</span>
            <span class="post-time">há 6 dias</span>
          </div>
          <span class="post-flair">Pergunta</span>
          <h2 class="post-title">Existe alguma casa de acolhimento em Recife para mulheres com filhos pequenos?</h2>
          <p class="post-excerpt">Preciso de ajuda urgente. Tenho dois filhos e não tenho para onde ir. Alguém conhece alguma ONG ou abrigo na região metropolitana do Recife?</p>
          <div class="post-actions">
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">chat_bubble</span> 39 Comentários</button>
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">share</span> Compartilhar</button>
            <button class="action-btn"><span class="icon">bookmark</span> Salvar</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
